fields.value: Current and future forage suitability maps for Ethiopia and Kenya

authorAffiliation.value: International Center for Tropical Agriculture - CIAT
International Center for Tropical Agriculture - CIAT

datasetContactAffiliation.value: International Center for Tropical Agriculture - CIAT

dsDescriptionValue.value: This data was produced using Targeting Tools – a web-based GIS tool, which matches a suitability criteria that include climate and environmental requirements for each of the forage varieties with a spatial database that’s comprises organic carbon, soil PH, annual precipitation, mean temperature, growing days and elevation data to characterize the suitability.
